| [Centre](/Centre_(department))        | [Hinche](/Hinche)        | 3,487      | 746,236     | 210                | Central         |
| [Grand'Anse](/Grand%27Anse_(department)) | [Jérémie](/J%C3%A9r%C3%A9mie) | 1,912      | 468,301     | 240                | South           |
| [Nippes](/Nippes)           | [Miragoâne](/Mirago%C3%A2ne) | 1,268      | 342,525     | 270                | South           |
| [Nord](/Nord_(Haitian_department))      | [Cap-Haïtien](/Cap-Ha%C3%AFtien) | 2,115      | 1,067,177   | 500                | North           |
