| [Ouest](/Ouest_(department))       | [Port-au-Prince](/Port-au-Prince) | 4,983      | 4,029,705   | 810                | West            |
| [Sud-Est](/Sud-Est_(department))     | [Jacmel](/Jacmel)        | 2,034      | 632,601     | 310                | West            |
