The density figures are particularly telling. The [Ouest](/Ouest_(department)) department, home to the capital, is by far the most densely populated, a common phenomenon in many nations. The [Nord](/Nord_(Haitian_department)) department also shows a significant population density, indicating established centers of habitation.

